<section class="section about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid reveal">
      <div class="about-left">
        <div class="about-image-wrap">
          <div class="about-image-glow"></div>
          <img src="/images/headshot.png" alt="Andrew Brown" class="about-image" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-meta">
          <div class="about-meta-item">
            <span class="about-meta-label">Location</span>
            <span class="about-meta-value">Youngstown, Ohio</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-meta-item">
            <span class="about-meta-label">Education</span>
            <div class="about-edu-group">
              <span class="about-meta-value">Franklin University</span>
              <span class="about-meta-sub">B.S. Cybersecurity &middot; Minor: AI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-edu-group">
              <span class="about-meta-value">SUNY Adirondack</span>
              <span class="about-meta-sub">A.S. Business Administration &amp; Management</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-meta-item">
            <span class="about-meta-label">Focus</span>
            <span class="about-meta-value">Software Engineering &amp; Security</span>
            <span class="about-meta-value about-meta-sub">Human-First AI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <span class="section-label">About</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">From the field to the full stack.</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I've been in the field — literally. ISP installations for Starry, NOC monitoring with PRTG 
          and Grafana, 50+ network deployments at ICS, and 3.5 years servicing electronic security systems 
          inside bank branches. Vault doors, alarm panels, IP cameras, the works.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Then I built <a href="https://github.com/WanderingAstronomer/Vociferous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">Vociferous</a> — 
          an offline speech-to-text desktop app, from scratch. 600 hours. 355 commits. 130 releases. 
          I led a team to <a href="/proofs/ncl/ncl-cyber-skyline-report-fall-team-2025.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link">20th out of 4,674 teams</a> 
          in the National Cyber League. I'm president of Franklin University's Programming SIG, 
          senior officer in the Cybersecurity SIG, and I've delivered 30+ presentations across both clubs.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          I care about what happens to people when they use software. Vociferous exists because it 
          shouldn't take an internet connection to transcribe your own voice. Every system I design 
          starts with the same question: what does the person on the other side of this actually need?
        </p>
        <p class="about-maxim">The right amount of complexity is the minimum needed for the current task.</p>
        <blockquote class="about-quote">
          <p>"...[Airplanes] are beautiful dreams. Engineers turn dreams into reality."</p>
          <footer class="about-quote-credit">— Hayao Miyazaki, <cite>The Wind Rises</cite></footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-image-wrap {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--amber));
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: 0;
    filter: blur(1px);
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 2px solid var(--bg-deep);
  }

  .about-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .about-meta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-meta-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-alternate);
  }

  .about-meta-sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-edu-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
  }

  .about-edu-group + .about-edu-group {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-link {
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s var(--ease-out);
  }

  .about-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .about-maxim {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.7;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    margin-block: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--cyan);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-quote-credit {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about-quote-credit cite {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .about-left {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-image-wrap {
      max-width: 200px;
    }

    .about-meta {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-meta-item {
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
